variable.name: CONSENT
variable.description: Consent group as determined by DAC. Use of this data is limited to Health/Biomedical/Medical purposes. This Consent Group does not preclude the use in studies of population origins and ancestry. This data may be used for health-related research focused on child health and development from childhood into adulthood and maternal health.
